title: Newly Renovated Unit, Wood Floors & Laundry On-Site - 2 Weeks Free
posting_body: ['Recently Updated Greenwood 2Bed - 2 Weeks Free', 'Property Address', '8737 GREENWOOD AVE N UNIT 1 | SEATTLE, WA 98103', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', '87th Greenwood Apartments - Seattle Property Management Associates', 'Description', "The 87th Greenwood Apartments is a charming 2 story building built in the late 60's.", 'It is located two blocks from the Greenwood Fred Meyer and a 2 blocks from 85th/Greenwood intersection where the Metro Bus stops every 15 minutes.', 'There is a plethora of shops and restaurants within walking distance as well as Sandel Park which is a great nearby spot to picnic or enjoy open space.', 'This newly renovated 2bed/1bath has beautiful refinished wood floors throughout, new vinyl in the kitchen, new kitchen cabinets and counter, new shower surround and vanity, as well as updated trim.', 'At the time of application, we require payment of the $25 application fee per person and a $1000 deposit that is then applied to the refundable security deposit upon approval.', 'For more information or to schedule a tour please call', 'show contact info', 'Amenities', 'Controlled Access', 'Secure Entry', 'On-Site Management', 'Laundry On Site', 'off-street parking', 'Wood Floors', 'New Flooring', 'Quartz Shower Surround', 'Granite Countertops', 'near transportation', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 730', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,725.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,000.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
